description: The Tucson Leather Storage Ottoman Coffee Table is a great way to help you organize your living room in a classic tasteful fashion. Over the years there have been as many Shabby Chic stores and product extensions always staying true to my core values and aesthetics...the beauty of imperfection.Our focus as the leading rustic brand who defined its own category and became the adjective of our aesthetic of products is to offer a luxury home furnishing line of products reminiscent of years gone by.Any piece of our furniture will serve the many rooms in your manor from bedroom living room dining room and kitchen. Our attention to detail and vintage influence are handpicked and inspired during my travels to Texas London and all places in between. I pride myself on continuing to sell products that gather memories and have the quality and aesthetics to become heirlooms. We use the best woods and construction available. We have buckets of dye in our workroom to create the perfect palette. We painstakingly restore vintage treasures while protecting the character of time worn beauties. All are a true labor of love. Tattered Elegance has a home in Rachel Ashwell Shabby Chic .Shabby Chic is a place where we can indulge in the time it takes to pay attention to every little detail from the perfect ruffle to the perfect paint finish and mushy cushion. And still after all these years I can be seen fluffing cushions or creating moments of magic we hope you do too.

title: TearDrop Side Table White Color with 18 inch Round Glass Top
description: This product is Manufactured By  Fab Glass and Mirror LLC  This stunning white teardrop glass side table features a round table top and unique base. The round Cocktail Table is wellbalanced for multifunctional use and will add to your contemporary or modern decor. Use one of these white end tables as a modern coffee table or to display artwork. It makes a lovely addition to a home bar office waiting room or living room area.  Medium Density Fiberboard (MDF) Base of this stylish Teardrop White Color Side Table looks like Raindrop and its made of MDF (Medium Density Fiberboard) material. This is high grade composite material that performs better than solid wood. Made from recycled wood fiber and resin MDF is machine dried and pressed to produce dense stable sheets. Its more reliable than solid wood and stands up better to change in heat and humidity.  Available Colors Black Red  Packaging  The TearDrop Side Table White Color is professionally packaged individually wrapped in Styrofoam and OPP plastic for protection before being boxed.  Clear glass  Our glass table tops are manufactured by using a curing process that yields no air bubbles in order to provide you with crystal clear perfection.   Flat Polish  The glass table top is made with a standard polished edge produced by a straight line rectilinear or CNC machine. This machine produces a fine flat polished and tempered 3/8 or 10mm thick with clear glass table top suitable for all furniture glass and frameless toughened panels.  Tempered Glass  The glass used to make this table is tempered glass which is toughened through a process of extreme heating and rapid cooling during manufacturing. Tempered glass is two or more times stronger than annealed glass. If broken tempered glass shatters into many small fragments in order to prevent serious injuries. Tempered glass is intended for use in any situation requiring superior strength and safety properties where standard glass poses a risk.  Decorative Features This TearDrop Side Table White Color features a seethrough top that shows off the unique base fully. The glass easily holds food and drink without any risk of stains. Use this glass top table for home or business for an informal dining area meeting space coffee table desk or in front of the TV.

Aniline Dyeing is the process of soaking the hides in transparent aniline dyes which allows color to absorb into the natural hide. Top Grain Aniline leather is then topical stain protected to minimize liquid absorption during every day use but does not require imitation grain stamping methods which imprint a Faux grain over the majority of the leather surface.
